WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:46.880
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:49.146
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:53.497 --> 00:00:53.874
We're excited to be here.

00:00:53.874 --> 00:00:58.926
We have a lot to talk about and pray about tonight.

00:00:58.926 --> 00:01:03.260
First off, I want to tell you a cool testimony.

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:12.609
This testimony was a shock and awe to me, but of course we all know that Jesus is wonderful.

00:01:12.609 --> 00:01:47.742
Several weeks ago, the Lord instructed me to go over to this gentleman's house, and He said, "I want you to go over and I want you to pray for him because the arteries of his heart are clogged and he doesn't know it.

00:01:47.742 --> 00:01:54.710
There's a blockage.

00:02:03.909 --> 00:02:05.680
" And He said, "I want you to go over and lay hands on him because in the natural, his heart is about ready to have a heart attack.

00:02:06.520 --> 00:02:11.799
" I had a vision where the Lord showed me his wife was a widow.

00:02:11.799 --> 00:02:14.182
She was alone and they're not that old.

00:02:23.728 --> 00:02:23.904
I mean, they're not elder elders, but they're not old.

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:29.389
I don't even think they're old enough to be my mom and my dad, do you?

00:02:29.389 --> 00:02:30.009
No.

00:02:30.009 --> 00:02:36.490
So, the Lord warned me about this man and He said, "I want you to go over there and pray for him.

00:02:36.490 --> 00:02:44.507
" Well, when I was there, I said, "I'm not trying to scare you, but this is what the Lord is telling me.

00:02:44.507 --> 00:02:48.840
So, I want to pray for you.

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:53.771
Is it okay if I pray for you?

00:02:53.771 --> 00:03:00.070
" Because I'm not just going to lay hands on anyone who doesn't want me to pray for them.

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:09.890
But he asked me when I walked in.

00:03:19.626 --> 00:03:19.920
He said, "Brandon, I felt inside that maybe you could pray for something that I'm having a need of.

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:33.420
" And I said, "Well, okay.

00:03:33.810 --> 00:03:41.1000
" He said, "I have two hernias in my body that are pretty severe, and I'm scheduled to have surgery.

00:03:42.604 --> 00:03:44.239
" I believe it was a couple of weeks out.

00:03:46.239 --> 00:03:55.566
And he said, "But I'm believing that if you pray for me and we agree together, that I'll be healed.

00:03:55.566 --> 00:04:01.149
" Because certain people know that the Lord has put healing in my hands.

00:04:01.149 --> 00:04:03.447
I don't make it a widely known thing.

00:04:03.447 --> 00:04:13.219
I know the Lord told me when Ralph Wilkerson touched my hands and he said, "These hands are going to have fire in them.

00:04:13.219 --> 00:04:19.100
" He touched my hands, he touched the palm of each one of my hands, and he said, "I'm putting a double portion of the anointing on my life on you.

00:04:19.100 --> 00:04:21.751
" This is Ralph Wilkerson at Melodyland Christian Center.

00:04:21.751 --> 00:04:25.049
Back in 2001 he did this.

00:04:32.100 --> 00:04:38.080
Ever since then, my hands get hot with fire, but I never know when it's going to happen when I'm praying for somebody.

00:04:38.613 --> 00:04:41.520
Sometimes it's like touching a cold stove.

00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:48.880
In this situation, he said, "Will you please pray for me for these hernias?

00:04:54.870 --> 00:04:55.120
" And I was like, "Okay, well, I came here to pray for your heart.

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:01.640
The Lord told me about your heart.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:05.105
" And he goes, "Wow.

00:05:05.876 --> 00:05:20.089
" I could see he was kind of concerned about it on his face, but I didn't want to make a big deal out of it or let him know what I saw in the spirit, which was that this man was about to die.

00:05:20.347 --> 00:05:22.423
And so I prayed for him.

00:05:25.404 --> 00:05:37.096
I put his hand on his groin area and I put my hand on top because it's awkward—I'm not going to touch a man like that.

00:05:37.302 --> 00:05:44.928
I prayed for him a prayer of faith and I laid hands on him.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:55.016
I didn't hear anything, just like it was with the man with the lungs who got healed and got two brand-new lungs.

00:05:55.016 --> 00:06:04.583
The doctor told him he was going to die and he needed a lung transplant.

00:06:04.583 --> 00:06:07.097
Anybody knows that story?

00:06:07.097 --> 00:06:08.920
I've told it before.

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:18.617
Well, a couple of weeks go by and my wife got a text from his wife.

00:06:18.617 --> 00:06:20.960
She said, "Good morning.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:41.867
I have to share a prayer report with you.

00:06:41.867 --> 00:06:48.080
My husband has been going to doctors for over two years.

00:06:51.450 --> 00:06:59.580
He was diagnosed with double hernias and they have been waiting on him to have surgery.

00:06:59.580 --> 00:07:07.573
He's been putting it off and had so much stress about having surgery for quite some time.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:14.136
He went again to a new doctor last month, right after he asked Brandon to pray for him.

00:07:14.136 --> 00:07:17.280
He had several tests and ultrasounds again.

00:07:21.706 --> 00:07:22.093
The results came back yesterday.

00:07:22.093 --> 00:07:23.390
It's a total answer to prayer.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:26.960
I had to share below a picture of the report findings.

00:07:28.080 --> 00:07:32.308
" The power of God touched him; the hernias are completely gone, both of them.

00:07:38.422 --> 00:07:38.810
And the doctor said, "You don't have to have surgery.

00:07:38.810 --> 00:07:45.840
All the hernia and all the evidence of the hernia, even through the ultrasound, is completely gone.

00:07:58.422 --> 00:07:58.651
" And he had had this and he was suffering.

00:07:58.651 --> 00:08:00.536
It hurt; he said it was very uncomfortable.

00:08:00.536 --> 00:08:13.531
Of course, he had two major hernias and they had scheduled him six weeks out from having the surgery because he was like, "I'm just going to go ahead and do it.

00:08:13.531 --> 00:08:23.480
" So the power of God touched him and I was just giving all the glory to the Lord for it.

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:24.200
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:08:27.208 --> 00:08:30.864
I went over there to give him the word about the heart and Jesus touches the hernias that were bothering him.

00:08:30.864 --> 00:08:33.600
I thought, we are in the last days.

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:36.068
I talked to my friend Billy Burke today.

00:08:36.068 --> 00:08:37.440
I love that man.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:50.613
I know for a fact what the Lord has shown me about his ministry and what's going to happen in the days ahead with great signs and wonders, even more than what he already walks in.

00:08:50.613 --> 00:09:02.959
But I know whenever the Lord told me "cross-pollination," when you start talking to people that walk underneath an anointing and you sow into their ministry and you believe by faith, it's a covenant.

00:09:10.320 --> 00:09:10.613
You start giving and you start believing.

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:20.480
I already know what the Lord has told me, that I'll walk in healings, but I don't know when it's going to come on like that full-time.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:31.420
All I know is the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm going to use you one day with this and I'll use Diana with you.

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:55.342
" And even Billy has given Diana words about how she'll pray for babies that are dead in the womb—where the mother has gotten a bad report of a baby that has been diagnosed as not alive anymore—and the power of God, by laying hands on the mother, is going to raise that baby from the dead.

00:09:55.342 --> 00:09:58.720
I truly believe that in the resurrection power of the Lord Jesus.

00:10:13.405 --> 00:10:13.736
I was so excited for him that he doesn't have to have surgery now and that he got such a great report.

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:23.406
I don't want things like that to ever just bypass you; I want to always stay in awe of Jesus for what He's done in these last days.

00:10:23.406 --> 00:10:25.040
Oh, Father, thank you.

00:10:26.423 --> 00:10:32.200
And like He said, "Brandon, never take a miracle for granted.

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:35.920
Never look at it as insignificant when I touch somebody.

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:43.610
For when there are so many miracles that are about to take place, don't become familiar with my glory.

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:53.493
Don't become familiar with what I'm doing in ministry.

00:11:02.800 --> 00:11:03.840
" I know beyond a shadow of a doubt.

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:06.720
I've seen dogs raised from the dead.

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:14.880
I've seen people carrying an oxygen tank behind them, completely grayed out on the verge of death.

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:19.970
I've laid hands on them and God gave them two brand-new lungs.

00:11:19.970 --> 00:11:20.960
They came back.

00:11:31.769 --> 00:11:32.133
The doctor said, "We're taking you off the donor's list," completely healed by the power of God.

00:11:32.133 --> 00:11:41.490
They were delivered after they sprayed Roundup on the ground for 40-some years for the city and breathing in all those chemicals every single day destroyed their lungs.

00:11:51.627 --> 00:11:51.840
He had an oxygen tank and ran up to me saying, "I've been healed.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:54.260
" I just came back to tell you.

00:12:07.360 --> 00:12:07.740
I didn't know who he was because he wasn't ashy-looking.

00:12:07.740 --> 00:12:09.451
His skin had pigment.

00:12:09.451 --> 00:12:12.809
He looked great and I'll never forget it.

00:12:22.631 --> 00:12:23.013
I thought, "Wow, Jesus.

00:12:23.013 --> 00:12:33.140
" As I went back into some of the things the Lord has shown us about healings and things that are about to take place, I thought of "can these bones live?

00:12:44.810 --> 00:12:45.260
" and the dead in Christ rising first.

00:12:45.260 --> 00:12:52.670
He said, "Randy, you don't realize that all that which remains will be caught up.

00:12:52.670 --> 00:12:57.813
You don't know there's a little bit of a gap there.

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:10.091
" There's a lot of people that talk about creation—that whenever God made the earth, there's a gap between the verses, between "let" and how the dinosaurs ruled in that time frame.

00:13:17.964 --> 00:13:20.516
I think Rick Renner teaches it.

00:13:20.516 --> 00:13:29.680
I'll butcher it; I am not a theological Greek person, but I know Rick Renner does that and he is very gifted at it.

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:40.640
He talks about creation and the gap.

00:13:40.640 --> 00:13:41.017
Dr.

00:13:41.017 --> 00:13:43.463
Carl Baugh, I believe, is who it was.

00:13:43.749 --> 00:13:48.512
I remember hearing him one day talking about the gap.

00:13:48.512 --> 00:13:55.160
But I was just trying to encourage you all that God's moving, shaking, and doing things.

00:14:03.280 --> 00:14:07.840
I have such an anticipation for these last days and what God's about to do.

00:14:07.840 --> 00:14:12.204
Billy was saying he was believing God to have a meeting here at the Mabee Center.

00:14:12.204 --> 00:14:13.368
Who would be interested?

00:14:13.584 --> 00:14:18.053
Let us know in the comments down below when you're on that live.

00:14:18.053 --> 00:14:26.000
Can you tell us if we had a meeting at ORU and we rented out the Mabee Center, would you come?

00:14:26.000 --> 00:14:30.720
I'm just curious before I take money and invest in it.

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:32.229
Would you come?

00:14:32.229 --> 00:14:35.279
Would you like to have a healing meeting?

00:14:35.279 --> 00:14:40.719
I'll be there and I'll have to have security, but Billy Burke's going to do the services.

00:14:40.719 --> 00:14:46.549
I'll be sitting in the congregation supporting him, praying, and enjoying the service.

00:14:47.888 --> 00:14:54.520
I won't be speaking, but I believe in my friend and the anointing on his life; I believe in the gift.

00:14:54.520 --> 00:14:56.423
It touches me.

00:14:56.423 --> 00:15:01.889
After Megan went to Eufaula, she no longer has plays in her periods; Jesus is touching her.

00:15:01.889 --> 00:15:05.519
That's why I get so many little nuggets from people.

00:15:06.969 --> 00:15:12.150
I always try to be a friend to authentic people that really truly love the Lord.

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:26.960
I just wanted to throw that out there.

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:36.430
I didn't know if there's anybody who would be interested in having a meeting, coming to Tulsa, and doing the Mabee Center at ORU.

00:15:40.480 --> 00:15:40.850
It holds 3,500 people.

00:15:45.097 --> 00:15:45.429
I wonder if we could fill it.

00:15:46.390 --> 00:15:47.230
I just truly believe we could.

00:15:47.230 --> 00:15:50.034
I believe there's going to be something.

00:15:52.533 --> 00:15:53.466
The Lord said, "It'll be a dome of glory there.

00:15:55.531 --> 00:16:01.440
It's going to be a time of glory over you.

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:05.224
" I thought, "What if this is the beginning of it?

00:16:05.224 --> 00:16:08.402
" because Billy brought it up to me today.

00:16:08.402 --> 00:16:12.639
He said, "It's been on my heart, Brandon.

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:15.720
I've been praying about it.

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:18.190
" He asked, "What do you feel?

00:16:18.190 --> 00:16:21.181
" I thought I'll pray about it, too.

00:16:21.181 --> 00:16:22.308
Let's do this.

00:16:22.308 --> 00:16:32.780
So, if you're interested and you put it in the comments, if you think, "Hey, I'd like to come to Tulsa and have a healing revival," let's do it.

00:16:32.780 --> 00:16:35.940
I thought what a time that would be to have it.

00:16:43.232 --> 00:16:43.488
He said, "I don't want to do it at a church or hotel.

00:16:43.488 --> 00:16:46.173
Maybe we could do it there at ORU.

00:16:46.173 --> 00:16:53.580
" So, we'll have to look into it and see if ORU would let us do it.

00:16:53.800 --> 00:17:05.703
I don't think we would fill up the Mabee Center there yet at 10,000, but I believe we could really fill up the 3,500.

00:17:05.703 --> 00:17:13.806
So, maybe I might need to stretch my faith that big.

00:17:13.806 --> 00:17:20.160
I just know that people are hungry and maybe you would want to be a part of it.

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:24.737
I'll bring that to you, and if you're interested, let us know.

00:17:24.737 --> 00:17:30.799
Also, I just want to say from the last video, I apologize for my attitude.

00:17:41.860 --> 00:17:42.160
I apologize for how I said the word and told everybody they could go to heck and the attitude that I had.

00:17:45.280 --> 00:17:52.179
The Lord really got onto me after it was over and said, "You don't represent me like that.

00:17:52.429 --> 00:17:53.939
You don't talk that way.

00:17:53.939 --> 00:17:55.240
" I'm ashamed of that.

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:59.429
I just want to tell you I apologize for how I handled that.

00:17:59.429 --> 00:18:05.896
I get under pressure, and it's like I told Billy.

00:18:05.896 --> 00:18:08.659
He said, "Brandon, it's okay.

00:18:19.240 --> 00:18:19.510
You were just ankle-deep that day.

00:18:19.510 --> 00:18:21.387
" We go from glory to glory.

00:18:21.387 --> 00:18:25.609
We go from ankle-deep to knee-deep to waist-deep to over the head.

00:18:25.609 --> 00:18:30.685
Just in that day, in that moment, my toes weren't even wet.

00:18:40.960 --> 00:18:41.440
I said, "You're being generous.

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:43.359
I wasn't ankle-deep.

00:18:43.359 --> 00:18:46.266
My toes weren't even wet, brother.

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:49.040
I was all in the flesh.

00:18:49.040 --> 00:18:55.800
" But I just wanted to ask you all to forgive me for being an idiot.

00:18:56.914 --> 00:18:57.188
I appreciate it.

00:18:59.013 --> 00:19:02.343
We're all a work in progress and Brandon still has issues.

00:19:02.343 --> 00:19:15.260
I work through things; I have things I get over with anger, yelling, and getting mad at stupid people on the road.

00:19:30.366 --> 00:19:30.651
You have to just calm yourself down and get in the Word more.

00:19:30.651 --> 00:19:45.279
It's like he said, when you're going through life and the devil's tempting you to get in the flesh, the only way he gets you is if you're empty.

00:19:45.279 --> 00:19:47.129
Let your full fight for you.

00:19:47.129 --> 00:19:58.629
The only way you're able to resist the devil is your word level and your spirit level—being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, being word and spirit.

00:20:06.251 --> 00:20:11.200
There's too much "word of faith" where it's out of kilter and you don't add the Spirit to it where you flow with the Holy Ghost and have the Word.

00:20:15.463 --> 00:20:18.254
You can't just be totally Word and you can't just be totally Holy Spirit; you get flaky.

00:20:27.040 --> 00:20:27.280
You have to have a balance.

00:20:27.280 --> 00:20:32.880
He instructed me: "As people that have temptations with anger, getting upset, or acting out...

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:43.180
" I get all kinds of messages: "Brandon, I'm dealing with addictions, drugs, alcohol, pornography, or lust.

00:20:43.180 --> 00:20:45.120
" It's a sign of being ankle-deep.

00:20:45.120 --> 00:20:47.510
We must stay filled in these last days.

00:20:47.510 --> 00:20:57.499
That was what the Lord was showing me even more today: "Brandon, you get low on the Word.

00:21:10.280 --> 00:21:10.550
" The less you are filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, the more you don't stay full.

00:21:10.550 --> 00:21:12.503
Let your full fight for you.

00:21:15.200 --> 00:21:21.487
The more you stay full, the more you can submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:21:21.487 --> 00:21:22.862
I just want to encourage everybody.

00:21:24.389 --> 00:21:27.138
The problem is if we don't know the truth, the truth won't set us free.

00:21:27.138 --> 00:21:31.173
The more you know the truth of God's Word, the truth will set you free.

00:21:31.173 --> 00:21:33.862
The entrance of His Word brings forth light.

00:21:33.862 --> 00:21:40.106
The light is illuminating; it brings forth that Holy Ghost and fire as you're reading the pages of this beautiful book.

00:21:47.167 --> 00:21:49.632
It becomes life and rhema knowledge over your mind the more you meditate on the Word of God.

00:21:49.632 --> 00:21:52.540
It will change you from the inside out.

00:21:52.750 --> 00:22:03.440
The fuller you get of God's Word, when you submit yourself unto God and you resist the devil, he will flee from you.

00:22:03.440 --> 00:22:07.929
But you have to learn that you have to get in that Word and yield yourself.

00:22:07.929 --> 00:22:10.498
How much do you need the Holy Spirit today?

00:22:14.743 --> 00:22:15.029
I need you.

00:22:16.951 --> 00:22:19.720
I depend on you.

00:22:19.720 --> 00:22:24.781
The moment you put your foot out of the bed onto the carpet: "I need you.

00:22:24.781 --> 00:22:25.715
Fill me.

00:22:31.644 --> 00:22:31.875
" You have to stay in that place of being filled.

00:22:42.098 --> 00:22:42.320
In these last days, you don't understand where we're headed.

00:22:42.320 --> 00:22:47.067
You don't understand the "shaking to awaken" that we're about to experience in this generation.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:50.320
The Lord said very sobering days are coming.

00:22:50.320 --> 00:23:02.280
But if you understand Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 and you understand how to be filled with the Holy Ghost to the overflow—not just being weird, but surrendering all to him.

00:23:02.280 --> 00:23:06.735
Surrender all to him today and say, "I need you.

00:23:21.359 --> 00:23:21.760
" The moment you recognize that you need him, you realize our dependency on him.

00:23:21.760 --> 00:23:24.462
I can't do this without you.

00:23:24.462 --> 00:23:26.720
I'm sold out to Jesus.

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:47.160
When you talk to elders and people who have lived ministry for a long time—years and years, more than I've been alive—and you talk to people that are still going, you learn from people that have fruit, that are still going strong in their almost 80s.

00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:50.040
You go, "Hey, there's something more to what you're saying.

00:23:50.040 --> 00:23:52.260
I've got to learn this.

00:23:52.260 --> 00:23:53.520
" Stay full.

00:23:53.520 --> 00:23:54.780
Stay full.

00:23:54.780 --> 00:24:04.684
There are so many times that you say, "Well, I'm dealing with this.

00:24:19.359 --> 00:24:19.639
I'm dealing with that.

00:24:21.103 --> 00:24:21.696
I can't get over this.

00:24:21.696 --> 00:24:24.983
" Call those things that be not as though they were.

00:24:24.983 --> 00:24:37.863
But the only way you do that is knowing who you are in Christ and by sitting at His feet and basking in His presence on a day-to-day basis.

00:24:38.667 --> 00:24:48.420
I told you Jesus said, "It is written, Satan, man shall not live by bread, but every word that proceedeth out of the mouth of the Father.

00:24:48.420 --> 00:24:56.549
" When the devil tried to tempt Him, "Turn this stone into bread, Jesus," but Jesus dealt with flesh just like every single one of us.

00:24:56.549 --> 00:25:00.159
Jesus was man; He was God created in flesh.

00:25:00.159 --> 00:25:04.063
But He dealt with temptations, heartache, and pain.

00:25:04.063 --> 00:25:09.400
Billy said people don't want to talk about John 7.

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:16.818
I remember what the verse was—he talked about how Jesus had to flee because the religious people were trying to kill Him.

00:25:16.818 --> 00:25:30.266
He had to flee for a season, and he said a lot of people won't want to talk about that, but the Bible clearly says that Jesus had to go away because it wasn't His time yet.

00:25:30.266 --> 00:25:33.702
They tried to kill Him before His time.

00:25:40.479 --> 00:25:40.639
He talks about it because I was talking about having to hire security and all this stuff.

00:25:48.728 --> 00:25:48.976
I said, "Is that fear?

00:25:49.472 --> 00:25:51.547
" And he's like, "Brandon, no, I think it's wisdom.

00:26:03.360 --> 00:26:03.680
" So, I'm hiring full-time security.

00:26:03.680 --> 00:26:06.890
I've got people that are—what was it?

00:26:06.890 --> 00:26:09.039
Is it this one?

